The evidence with the title 'How badly has the Obama era damaged the Democratic party ... ' says Nov 4, 2015  ... Under president Obama , Democrats have lost 900+ state legislature seats, 12 governors , 69 House seats, 13 Senate seats.  ... Tally up those losses by comparing the number of House and Senate seats Dems held when Barack Obama took office on Inauguration Day 2009 with the number they hold today . 
